rComments: Greek mythology class is wonderful with her. Learnt a lot of stuff and she is clearly interested in what she's teaching. I only wish we would have written exams, not multiple choice... However, the class was so large it would have taken forever to correct all of them!

Nice and friendly, but knowledge seems spotty.  She made numerous errors throughout the semester in marking exams and assignments and even just in taking up exercises.  Not dynamic enough personality to make DGDs interesting or worth attending regularly.
